Package: PortfolioTesteR
Type: Package
Title: Test Investment Strategies with English-Like Code
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alberto Pallotta
Maintainer: Alberto Pallotta <pallottaalberto@gmail.com>
Description: Tools to design, backtest, and analyze portfolio strategies using
    simple, English-like function chains. Includes momentum, RSI, regime filters,
    position limits, and multiple weighting schemes with plotting and summaries.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    data.table,
    graphics,
    quantmod,
    RSQLite,
    stats,
    TTR,
    utils,
    zoo
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/alb3rtazzo/PortfolioTesteR
BugReports: https://github.com/alb3rtazzo/PortfolioTesteR/issues

